                              <p><strong>Specialty Treatment Gift Certificates</strong><br>
                                These Gift Certificates include use of the Health Club on the day of the massage and may be upgraded to include gratuity. These Gift Certificates may be redeemed only for the treatment for which they are purchased.</p>
                              <ul>
                                <li>Hot Stone (30 min.) &ndash; $90 Treatment Only / $110 with Gratuity </li>
                                <li>Salt Glow (45 min.) &ndash; $125 Treatment Only / $145 with Gratuity </li>
